    "description": "Enjoy the BIC 2024 exhibition game “OVER ROAD” on Steam!<br><br>“OVER ROAD” is a game where a household robot that lost its owner in a sudden disaster<br>floats into the air and moves through the destroyed roads with one robot arm.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Grab action on destroyed roads</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190910/extras/6c7642bf6aa5b5e5ee48fa356e723496.poster.avif?t=1760585003\" width=616 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190910/extras/6c7642bf6aa5b5e5ee48fa356e723496.webm?t=1760585003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190910/extras/6c7642bf6aa5b5e5ee48fa356e723496.mp4?t=1760585003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>From safety poles to CCTV, the roads are full of robots that don't like fragile household robots.<br>“Pull” and “drag” with your robot arm to avoid danger and move through the roads.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How home robots solve problems</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190910/extras/b460af65396f30dc490c84c6383f5bf3.poster.avif?t=1760585003\" width=616 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190910/extras/b460af65396f30dc490c84c6383f5bf3.webm?t=1760585003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190910/extras/b460af65396f30dc490c84c6383f5bf3.mp4?t=1760585003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>If you manage to get through the line of fire and grab the enemy, their weapon is now in your hands.<br>Grab the safety pole to shoot a laser, and grab the CCTV to jump far!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Towards the end of the collapsed city</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190910/extras/1f629fdd4f7f850287dbb30bcaa6e313.poster.avif?t=1760585003\" width=616 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190910/extras/1f629fdd4f7f850287dbb30bcaa6e313.webm?t=1760585003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190910/extras/1f629fdd4f7f850287dbb30bcaa6e313.mp4?t=1760585003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>When the power is turned on, all that remains is the coordinates of the last detected location of the owner.<br>Can the small household robot meet its owner again along the shattered road?",
